    new_data = pd.DataFrame([[hash_password(user_password), date, category, amount, description]],
                            columns=["User Password", "Date", "Category", "Amount", "Description"])
    df = pd.concat([df, new_data], ignore_index=True)
    df["Date"] = pd.to_datetime(df["Date"])

def delete_entry(user_password, entry_index):
    df = load_data()
    user_df = df[df["User Password"] == hash_password(user_password)]
    if entry_index < len(user_df):
        user_df = user_df.drop(user_df.index[entry_index])
        df = df[df["User Password"] != hash_password(user_password)]
        df = pd.concat([df, user_df], ignore_index=True)
        df.to_csv(USER_DATA_FILE, index=False)
        return True
    return False
